&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-family: helvetica, arial, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;This is a highly visible leadership role with direct influence on Chime&#39;s growth strategy, product roadmap, and design culture. If you&#39;re energized by building high-performing teams, solving ambiguous growth challenges, and reimagining how design organizations operate in the age of AI, we&#39;d love to hear from you.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
